defines linkage for the following 
<code><font color="blue">mat2cpp</font></code> namespace functions:

<table><tr><td align='left'  valign='top'>

<code><font color="blue">abs</font></code>         </td><td align='left'  valign='top'>
 <a href="element_unary.xml" target="_top">Matlab or Octave Elementwise Unary Functions</a> </td></tr><tr><td align='left'  valign='top'>

<code><font color="blue">log</font></code>         </td><td align='left'  valign='top'>
 <a href="element_unary.xml" target="_top">Matlab or Octave Elementwise Unary Functions</a> </td></tr><tr><td align='left'  valign='top'>

<code><font color="blue">diag_prod</font></code>   </td><td align='left'  valign='top'>
 <a href="diag_prod.xml" target="_top">Diagonal Matrix Product with General Matrix</a>     </td></tr><tr><td align='left'  valign='top'>

<code><font color="blue">matrix_div</font></code>  </td><td align='left'  valign='top'>
 <a href="matrix_div.xml" target="_top">Matrix Division</a>    </td></tr><tr><td align='left'  valign='top'>

<code><font color="blue">max</font></code>         </td><td align='left'  valign='top'>
 <a href="max.xml" target="_top">Maximum Element of a Matrix</a>           </td></tr><tr><td align='left'  valign='top'>

<code><font color="blue">min</font></code>         </td><td align='left'  valign='top'>
